00:00 False Report: Indiana Jones Reboot Not in Development (For Now)
These headlines caused a stir: "Disney is working on an Indiana Jones reboot! A new actor is set to take on the role!" The source of the rumors: The DisInsider – a website specializing in Disney leaks…

01:53 Dune 3: Filming Has Begun!
Finally! Filming for the grand finale of the "Dune" saga has begun. According to Variety, the title of the blockbuster has also been revealed: It is simply "Dune: Part Three".

03:26 New Trailers
This week, two new trailers took center stage. First, the full trailer for the new "Wednesday" season at Nevermore Academy sparked a lot of excitement among you. The trailer for the new SpongeBob movie "Search for SquarePants", however, received mixed reactions...
